sql:
SELECT source_name
FROM network_sources
WHERE operational_status = 'operational';

SELECT PDR
FROM network_metrics
WHERE seed = 0 AND source_id = 0;

SELECT SUM(geocast_packets) AS total_geocast_packets
FROM network_metrics
WHERE seed = 1;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS active_mr_nodes
FROM mr_nodes
WHERE status = 'active';

external_knowledge:
- Packet delivery ratio (PDR) of 1 indicates 100% successful packet delivery; 
- Operational status 'operational' means the source is currently in service; 
- Active mobile router nodes are those that are currently running and functional; 
- Users with 'view_metrics' and 'edit_metrics' permissions can both view and edit network metrics; 
- Time range '2023-10-01 00:00:00' to '2023-10-01 23:59:59' includes the entire day of October 1, 2023.

sql:
SELECT AVG(latency) AS average_latency
FROM network_metrics
WHERE source_id = 0;

SELECT source_id, AVG(latency) AS average_latency
FROM network_metrics
GROUP BY source_id;
